<doc id="938731" wikidata="Q4437846" url="?curid=938731" title="List of Battlestar Galactica (1978 TV series) and Galactica 1980 episodes">
<text>&quot;Battlestar Galactica&quot; is an American science fiction television series created by Glen A. Larson that aired on the ABC network from September 17, 1978, to April 29, 1979. It stars an ensemble cast led by Richard Hatch, Dirk Benedict and Lorne Greene. Canceled after 24 episodes, the series was revived as &quot;Galactica 1980&quot;, which aired for 10 episodes from January 27 to May 4, 1980.

The series follows a group of humans fleeing the destruction of their homeworlds aboard the titular spacecraft, searching for a new home while being pursued by the Cylons, a fearsome society of robots intent on exterminating all humans.

