Note: the arrange versions of &quot;Zero 2&quot; and &quot;Zero 2 Alpha&quot; are the versions used in the US release, so &quot;Alpha Anthology&quot; only has two extra games (&quot;SFA3 Upper&quot; and &quot;Hyper SFA&quot;).

